projects.title: Generating Synthetic Data Using GANs
projects.description: Generative Adversarial Network project for creating realistic synthetic datasets, addressing data scarcity and privacy concerns in machine learning workflows
projects.longDescription: A deep learning project using Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) to generate synthetic tabular data that preserves the statistical properties of the original dataset, useful for data augmentation, privacy-preserving analytics, and ML model training

projects.title: US Healthcare Analysis - Power BI
projects.description: Interactive Power BI dashboard analyzing US healthcare data to uncover trends in patient outcomes, hospital performance, and cost efficiency
projects.longDescription: A healthcare analytics project leveraging Power BI to build interactive dashboards that visualize key healthcare metrics including patient demographics, readmission rates, treatment costs, and hospital performance indicators across the US healthcare system

projects.title: Nursing Home Financial Analysis
projects.description: Financial performance analysis of nursing home facilities, evaluating revenue trends, cost structures, and operational efficiency metrics
projects.longDescription: A financial analytics project examining nursing home facility data to assess profitability, cost drivers, revenue patterns, and operational efficiency, providing actionable insights for healthcare administrators and financial stakeholders

projects.title: Dashboards Development - Tableau & Power BI
projects.description: Collection of interactive dashboards built using Tableau and Power BI for business intelligence, data storytelling, and executive reporting
projects.longDescription: A portfolio of interactive business intelligence dashboards developed using Tableau and Power BI, demonstrating data visualization best practices, KPI monitoring, trend analysis, and executive-level reporting across multiple domains
